PrecisAppointment of MARY LOUISE BERNARD, of Wagmatcook Reserve, Cape Breton, Nova Scotia, INDIRA V. SAMARASEKERA, of Vancouver, British Columbia, and JUDITH A. WHITTICK, of St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador, as members of the Canada Foundation for Sustainable Development Technology, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years, effective March 22, 2002.
